response.overview: July 24, 2010 :: Dragon Gate USA presents Enter The Dragon 2010 as they celebrate their one year anniversary with a major appearance by the "American Dragon" himself, Bryan Danielson live from the "ECW" Arena in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania. Matches include:  -	Main Event  Bryan Danielson vs Shingo  -	Open the Freedom Gate Title Match  BxB Hulk (Champion) vs Masaaki Mochizuki  -	Rich Swann vs Scott Reed  -	Elimination Tag Team Match  YAMATO, Akira Tozawa, Jon Moxley & Gran Akuma vs Masato Yoshino, Mike Quackenbush, Jigsaw & Hallowicked  -	Naruki Doi vs Drake Younger  -	Chuck Taylor vs Ricochet vs Arik Cannon vs Adam Cole  -	CIMA vs Johnny Gargano
response.title: DGUSA Enter The Dragon 2010
